# 侧边栏切换按钮调整完成

侧边栏切换按钮已成功重新定位并调整样式，从浮动圆形按钮改为更符合 iOS 设计规范的长条形按钮，并优化了折叠状态下的交互体验。

## 变更内容

### 1. 侧边栏展开状态 (Expanded)
- **新位置**：位于“资源管理”标题下方，首个分类按钮（Mod）上方。
- **新样式**：采用长条形“胶囊”设计，背景在悬浮和选中时有微妙的半透明反馈。
- **文案**：使用“⬅️  收起侧栏”作为明确的操作指引。

### 2. 侧边栏折叠状态 (Collapsed)
- **改进**：在侧边栏折叠后，顶部保留了一个圆形的“展开”按钮，允许用户随时恢复侧边栏。
- **功能**：与展开状态下的切换按钮同步，通过 ViewModel 中的 `IsSidebarCollapsed` 属性进行统一状态管理。

### 3. 技术优化与问题修复
- **MVVM 绑定**：侧边栏的展开/折叠状态现在完全由 ViewModel 驱动，提高了代码的可维护性。
- **构建错误修复 (MC4011)**：解决了由于 `Storyboard.TargetName` 在 `Style` 中跨命名空间引用导致的构建失败（MC4011）。通过将动画逻辑直接集成到子组件的 `Style` 中，确保了 XAML 的合法性。
- **结构完整性**：修复了 XAML 结构中缺失的闭合标签，确保页面渲染与构建完全正常。
- **动画增强**：优化了 `SidebarBorder` 的宽度过渡动画，确保分类按钮和切换按钮在缩放过程中的视觉平滑度。

## 验证结果

- [x] 成功切换分类而不受侧边栏状态影响。
- [x] 展开/收起动画平滑，无布局跳动。
- [x] 修复了之前存在的 XAML 语法错误，页面加载正常。

```diff:ResourcesPage.xaml
<Page x:Class="GeminiLauncher.Views.ResourcesPage"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:ui="http://schemas.lepo.co/wpfui/2022/xaml"
      xmlns:vm="clr-namespace:GeminiLauncher.ViewModels"
      xmlns:conv="clr-namespace:GeminiLauncher.Converters"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="700" d:DesignWidth="1000"
      Title="Resources"
      Background="Transparent">

    <Page.DataContext>
        <vm:ResourcesViewModel/>
    </Page.DataContext>

    <Page.Resources>
        <BooleanToVisibilityConverter x:Key="BooleanToVisibilityConverter"/>
        <conv:InverseBooleanToVisibilityConverter x:Key="InverseBooleanToVisibilityConverter"/>
        <conv:CategoryNameConverter x:Key="CategoryNameConverter"/>
        <conv:StringMatchToBoolConverter x:Key="StringMatchToBoolConverter"/>
        
        <!-- 淡入动画 Storyboard -->
        <Storyboard x:Key="FadeInStoryboard">
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity"
                           From="0" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.4"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.7"/>
        </Storyboard>
        
        <!-- 滑动淡入动画 -->
        <Storyboard x:Key="SlideInStoryboard">
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TranslateTransform.Y)"
                           From="30" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.5"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.8"/>
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity"
                           From="0" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.5"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.7"/>
        </Storyboard>
    </Page.Resources>

    <Page.Triggers>
        <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="Page.Loaded">
            <BeginStoryboard Storyboard="{StaticResource FadeInStoryboard}"/>
        </EventTrigger>
    </Page.Triggers>

    <Grid>
        <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="220"/>
            <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
        </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

        <!-- LEFT SIDEBAR: Categories -->
        <Border Grid.Column="0" 
                Background="{DynamicResource iOS26.SidebarLayer}"
                CornerRadius="0,20,20,0"
                Margin="0,0,10,0">
            <StackPanel Margin="15,40,15,20">
                <TextBlock Text="资源管理" 
                         FontSize="14" 
                         FontWeight="SemiBold" 
                         Opacity="0.5" 
                         Foreground="White"
                         Margin="15,0,0,25"/>

                <StackPanel>
                    <StackPanel.Resources>
                        <Style x:Key="CategoryBtn" TargetType="Button">
                            <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                            <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
                            <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="White"/>
                            <Setter Property="HorizontalContentAlignment" Value="Left"/>
                            <Setter Property="Padding" Value="15,12"/>
                            <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,0,0,4"/>
                            <Setter Property="Cursor" Value="Hand"/>
                            <Setter Property="Template">
                                <Setter.Value>
                                    <ControlTemplate TargetType="Button">
                                        <Border x:Name="border" 
                                                Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" 
                                                CornerRadius="12">
                                            <ContentPresenter/>
                                        </Border>
                                        <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#15FFFFFF"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                        </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    </ControlTemplate>
                                </Setter.Value>
                            </Setter>
                        </Style>
                        
                        <!-- ToggleButton style for active state -->
                        <Style x:Key="CategoryToggle" TargetType="RadioButton">
                            <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                            <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
                            <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="White"/>
                            <Setter Property="HorizontalContentAlignment" Value="Left"/>
                            <Setter Property="Padding" Value="15,12"/>
                            <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,0,0,4"/>
                            <Setter Property="Cursor" Value="Hand"/>
                            <Setter Property="Template">
                                <Setter.Value>
                                    <ControlTemplate TargetType="RadioButton">
                                        <Border x:Name="border" 
                                                Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" 
                                                CornerRadius="12">
                                            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                                                <!-- Selection Indicator -->
                                                <Border x:Name="indicator" 
                                                        Width="4" Height="16" 
                                                        Background="#00E676" 
                                                        CornerRadius="2" 
                                                        Margin="0,0,10,0"
                                                        Visibility="Hidden"/>
                                                <ContentPresenter Margin="0,0,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </Border>
                                        <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#10FFFFFF"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#25FFFFFF"/>
                                                <Setter TargetName="indicator" Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                                                <Setter Property="FontWeight" Value="SemiBold"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                        </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    </ControlTemplate>
                                </Setter.Value>
                            </Setter>
                        </Style>
                    </StackPanel.Resources>

                    <RadioButton Content="🧩  Mod" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=mod}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="mod"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="📦  整合包" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=modpack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="modpack"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="🖼️  资源包" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=resourcepack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="resourcepack"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="☀️  光影包" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=shader}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="shader"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="🏷️  数据包" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=datapack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="datapack"/>
                </StackPanel>
            </StackPanel>
        </Border>

        <!-- RIGHT CONTENT AREA -->
        <Grid Grid.Column="1" Margin="30,30,40,30">
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <!-- Header Section -->
            <StackPanel Grid.Row="0" Margin="0,0,0,20">
                <!-- Title Row -->
                <Grid Margin="0,0,0,15">
                    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

                    <StackPanel Grid.Column="0">
                        <TextBlock Text="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource CategoryNameConverter}}" 
                                 FontSize="32" 
                                 FontWeight="Bold" 
                                 Foreground="White"
                                 Margin="0,0,0,5"/>
                        <TextBlock Text="从 Modrinth 仓库搜索和下载资源。" 
                                 FontSize="14" 
                                 Foreground="#B0FFFFFF"/>
                    </StackPanel>

                    <!-- Import Button -->
                    <ui:Button Grid.Column="1"
                               VerticalAlignment="Top"
                               Icon="{ui:SymbolIcon ArrowImport24}"
                               Content="导入 .mrpack"
                               Appearance="Primary"
                               Command="{Binding ImportModpackCommand}"/>
                </Grid>
                    
                <!-- Search Bar Card -->
                <Border Background="#40252525" 
                        BorderBrush="#60FFFFFF"
                        BorderThickness="1"
                        CornerRadius="12"
                        Padding="20,12">
                    <Border.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="20" ShadowDepth="0" Opacity="0.2" Color="Black"/>
                    </Border.Effect>
                    
                    <Grid>
                        <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                        </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                        
                        <!-- Search TextBox -->
                        <TextBox Grid.Column="0"
                                 Text="{Binding SearchQuery, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}"
                                 FontSize="16"
                                 VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                 Background="Transparent"
                                 BorderThickness="0"
                                 Foreground="#EEEEEE"
                                 CaretBrush="#00E676"
                                 Padding="5,8">
                            <TextBox.InputBindings>
                                <KeyBinding Key="Return" Command="{Binding SearchCommand}"/>
                            </TextBox.InputBindings>
                        </TextBox>
                        
                        <!-- Search Button -->
                        <ui:Button Grid.Column="1"
                                  Command="{Binding SearchCommand}"
                                  Content="🔍 搜索"
                                  Appearance="Secondary"
                                  Margin="10,0,0,0"
                                  Padding="20,8"
                                  Foreground="#EEEEEE"/>
                    </Grid>
                </Border>
                
                <!-- Progress Bar -->
                <ProgressBar IsIndeterminate="{Binding IsBusy}" 
                            Height="2" 
                            Margin="0,10,0,0"
                            Visibility="{Binding IsBusy, Converter={StaticResource BooleanToVisibilityConverter}}"
                            Background="Transparent" 
                            BorderThickness="0" 
                            Foreground="#00E676"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <!-- Main Content Area -->
            <ScrollViewer Grid.Row="1" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled">
                <Grid>
                    <!-- ========== FEATURED SECTIONS (when no search) ========== -->
                    <StackPanel Visibility="{Binding HasSearchResults, Converter={StaticResource InverseBooleanToVisibilityConverter}}">
                        
                        <!-- 🔥 Trending Section -->
                        <TextBlock Text="🔥 热门推荐" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="White" Margin="0,10,0,15"/>
                        <ScrollViewer HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Margin="0,0,0,30">
                            <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding TrendingMods}">
                                <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal"/>
                                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                    <DataTemplate>
                                        <Border Width="220" Height="280" Margin="0,0,15,0" 
                                                CornerRadius="16" 
                                                Background="#40252525" 
                                                BorderBrush="#60FFFFFF" 
                                                BorderThickness="1"
                                                RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5"
                                                Cursor="Hand">
                                            <Border.RenderTransform>
                                                <TransformGroup>
                                                    <ScaleTransform/>
                                                    <TranslateTransform/>
                                                </TransformGroup>
                                            </Border.RenderTransform>
                                            <Border.Effect>
                                                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="15" ShadowDepth="3" Opacity="0.3" Color="Black"/>
                                            </Border.Effect>
                                            <Border.Triggers>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseEnter">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="-3" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseLeave">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                            </Border.Triggers>
                                            <Grid>
                                                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="120"/>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                                    <Border.Background>
                                                        <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                                    </Border.Background>
                                                </Border>
                                                <StackPanel Grid.Row="1" Margin="15,12,15,15">
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" Foreground="White" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis" Margin="0,0,0,4"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" Margin="0,0,0,6"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Summary}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#80FFFFFF" TextWrapping="Wrap" MaxHeight="40" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                    <ui:Button Content="⬇️ 下载"
                                                               Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                               CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                               Appearance="Primary"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                               Margin="0,8,0,0"
                                                               Padding="0,6"
                                                               FontSize="12"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </Border>
                                    </DataTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl>
                        </ScrollViewer>

                        <!-- ✨ Newest Section -->
                        <TextBlock Text="✨ 最新发布" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold" Foreground="White" Margin="0,0,0,15"/>
                        <ScrollViewer HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Margin="0,0,0,30">
                            <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding NewestMods}">
                                <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal"/>
                                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                    <DataTemplate>
                                        <Border Width="220" Height="280" Margin="0,0,15,0" 
                                                CornerRadius="16" 
                                                Background="#40252525" 
                                                BorderBrush="#60FFFFFF" 
                                                BorderThickness="1"
                                                RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5"
                                                Cursor="Hand">
                                            <Border.RenderTransform>
                                                <TransformGroup>
                                                    <ScaleTransform/>
                                                    <TranslateTransform/>
                                                </TransformGroup>
                                            </Border.RenderTransform>
                                            <Border.Effect>
                                                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="15" ShadowDepth="3" Opacity="0.3" Color="Black"/>
                                            </Border.Effect>
                                            <Border.Triggers>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseEnter">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="-3" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseLeave">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                            </Border.Triggers>
                                            <Grid>
                                                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="120"/>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                                    <Border.Background>
                                                        <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                                    </Border.Background>
                                                </Border>
                                                <StackPanel Grid.Row="1" Margin="15,12,15,15">
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="15" Foreground="White" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis" Margin="0,0,0,4"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" Margin="0,0,0,6"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Summary}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#80FFFFFF" TextWrapping="Wrap" MaxHeight="40" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                    <ui:Button Content="⬇️ 下载"
                                                               Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                               CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                               Appearance="Primary"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                               Margin="0,8,0,0"
                                                               Padding="0,6"
                                                               FontSize="12"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </Border>
                                    </DataTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl>
                        </ScrollViewer>
                    </StackPanel>

                    <!-- ========== SEARCH RESULTS (after search) ========== -->
                    <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding SearchResults}"
                                Visibility="{Binding HasSearchResults, Converter={StaticResource BooleanToVisibilityConverter}}">
                        <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                            <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                <WrapPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Left"/>
                            </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                        </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                        <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            <DataTemplate>
                                <!-- Mod Card with Hover Animation -->
                                <Border Width="280" Height="360" Margin="15" 
                                        CornerRadius="16" 
                                        Background="#40252525" 
                                        BorderBrush="#60FFFFFF" 
                                        BorderThickness="1"
                                        RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5"
                                        Cursor="Hand">
                                    <Border.RenderTransform>
                                        <TransformGroup>
                                            <ScaleTransform/>
                                            <TranslateTransform/>
                                        </TransformGroup>
                                    </Border.RenderTransform>
                                    <Border.Effect>
                                        <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="20" ShadowDepth="5" Opacity="0.3" Color="Black"/>
                                    </Border.Effect>
                                    
                                    <!-- Hover Animation Triggers -->
                                    <Border.Triggers>
                                        <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseEnter">
                                            <BeginStoryboard>
                                                <Storyboard>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.05" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.05" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="-5" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                </Storyboard>
                                            </BeginStoryboard>
                                        </EventTrigger>
                                        <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseLeave">
                                            <BeginStoryboard>
                                                <Storyboard>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                </Storyboard>
                                            </BeginStoryboard>
                                        </EventTrigger>
                                    </Border.Triggers>
                                    
                                    <Grid>
                                        <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                            <RowDefinition Height="180"/>
                                            <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                        </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                        
                                        <!-- Cover Image -->
                                        <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                            <Border.Background>
                                                <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                            </Border.Background>
                                            <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
                                            <Border Background="Transparent">
                                                <Border.OpacityMask>
                                                    <LinearGradientBrush StartPoint="0,0.7" EndPoint="0,1">
                                                        <GradientStop Color="Transparent" Offset="0"/>
                                                        <GradientStop Color="#80000000" Offset="1"/>
                                                    </LinearGradientBrush>
                                                </Border.OpacityMask>
                                            </Border>
                                        </Border>
                                        
                                        <!-- Content Section -->
                                        <Grid Grid.Row="1" Margin="20,15,20,20">
                                            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                                            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                            
                                            <TextBlock Grid.Row="0" Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="18" Foreground="#FFFFFF" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis" Margin="0,0,0,5"/>
                                            <TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="13" Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" Margin="0,0,0,10"/>
                                            <TextBlock Grid.Row="2" Text="{Binding Summary}" FontSize="13" Foreground="#90FFFFFF" TextWrapping="Wrap" MaxHeight="60" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                            
                                            <!-- Download Button -->
                                            <ui:Button Grid.Row="3"
                                                      Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                      CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                      Content="⬇️ 下载"
                                                      Appearance="Primary"
                                                      HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                      Margin="0,10,0,0"
                                                      Padding="0,10"
                                                      FontWeight="SemiBold"/>
                                        </Grid>
                                    </Grid>
                                </Border>
                            </DataTemplate>
                        </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                    </ItemsControl>
                </Grid>
            </ScrollViewer>

            <!-- Import Progress Overlay -->
            <Grid Grid.Row="0" Grid.RowSpan="2" 
                  Background="#AA000000"
                  Visibility="{Binding IsImporting, Converter={StaticResource BooleanToVisibilityConverter}}"
                  Grid.ColumnSpan="2">
                <Border Background="#252525" 
                        BorderBrush="#40FFFFFF" 
                        BorderThickness="1" 
                        CornerRadius="16"
                        HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                        VerticalAlignment="Center"
                        Padding="30"
                        MinWidth="320">
                    <Border.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="20" ShadowDepth="0" Opacity="0.5" Color="Black"/>
                    </Border.Effect>
                    <StackPanel>
                        <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowImport24" FontSize="48" Foreground="White" Margin="0,0,0,15"/>
                        <TextBlock Text="正在导入整合包" 
                                   FontSize="20" 
                                   FontWeight="SemiBold" 
                                   Foreground="White" 
                                   HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                                   Margin="0,0,0,20"/>
                        
                        <ProgressBar Value="{Binding ImportProgress}" 
                                     Maximum="100" 
                                     Height="4" 
                                     Foreground="#00E676"
                                     Background="#33FFFFFF"
                                     BorderThickness="0"
                                     Margin="0,0,0,10"/>
                        
                        <TextBlock Text="{Binding ImportStatus}" 
                                   FontSize="13" 
                                   Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" 
                                   HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Border>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Page>
===
<Page x:Class="GeminiLauncher.Views.ResourcesPage"
      xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
      xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006" 
      xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008" 
      xmlns:ui="http://schemas.lepo.co/wpfui/2022/xaml"
      xmlns:vm="clr-namespace:GeminiLauncher.ViewModels"
      xmlns:conv="clr-namespace:GeminiLauncher.Converters"
      mc:Ignorable="d" 
      d:DesignHeight="700" d:DesignWidth="1000"
      Title="Resources"
      Background="Transparent">

    <Page.DataContext>
        <vm:ResourcesViewModel/>
    </Page.DataContext>

    <Page.Resources>
        <BooleanToVisibilityConverter x:Key="BooleanToVisibilityConverter"/>
        <conv:InverseBooleanToVisibilityConverter x:Key="InverseBooleanToVisibilityConverter"/>
        <conv:CategoryNameConverter x:Key="CategoryNameConverter"/>
        <conv:StringMatchToBoolConverter x:Key="StringMatchToBoolConverter"/>
        
        <!-- 淡入动画 Storyboard -->
        <Storyboard x:Key="FadeInStoryboard">
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity"
                           From="0" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.4"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.7"/>
        </Storyboard>
        
        <!-- 滑动淡入动画 -->
        <Storyboard x:Key="SlideInStoryboard">
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TranslateTransform.Y)"
                           From="30" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.5"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.8"/>
            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity"
                           From="0" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.5"
                           DecelerationRatio="0.7"/>
        </Storyboard>
    </Page.Resources>

    <Page.Triggers>
        <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="Page.Loaded">
            <BeginStoryboard Storyboard="{StaticResource FadeInStoryboard}"/>
        </EventTrigger>
    </Page.Triggers>

    <Grid>
        <!-- DASHBOARD LAYER (Sidebar + Main Content) -->
        <Grid x:Name="DashboardLayer">
            <Grid.Style>
                <Style TargetType="Grid">
                    <Style.Triggers>
                        <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsFullPageView}" Value="True">
                            <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                <BeginStoryboard>
                                    <Storyboard>
                                        <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                        <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.3">
                                            <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Hidden}"/>
                                        </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                    </Storyboard>
                                </BeginStoryboard>
                            </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                            <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                <BeginStoryboard>
                                    <Storyboard>
                                        <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility">
                                            <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                        </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                        <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.4"/>
                                    </Storyboard>
                                </BeginStoryboard>
                            </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                        </DataTrigger>
                    </Style.Triggers>
                </Style>
            </Grid.Style>
            
            <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
            </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

        <!-- LEFT SIDEBAR: Categories -->
        <Border Grid.Column="0" 
                x:Name="SidebarBorder"
                Background="{DynamicResource iOS26.SidebarLayer}"
                CornerRadius="0,20,20,0"
                Margin="0,0,10,0"
                HorizontalAlignment="Left">
            <Border.Style>
                <Style TargetType="Border">
                    <Setter Property="Width" Value="220"/>
                    <Style.Triggers>
                        <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsSidebarCollapsed}" Value="True">
                            <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                <BeginStoryboard>
                                    <Storyboard>
                                        <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Width" To="60" Duration="0:0:0.3">
                                            <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                                <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseInOut"/>
                                            </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                        </DoubleAnimation>
                                    </Storyboard>
                                </BeginStoryboard>
                            </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                            <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                <BeginStoryboard>
                                    <Storyboard>
                                        <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Width" To="220" Duration="0:0:0.3">
                                            <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                                <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseInOut"/>
                                            </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                        </DoubleAnimation>
                                    </Storyboard>
                                </BeginStoryboard>
                            </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                        </DataTrigger>
                    </Style.Triggers>
                </Style>
            </Border.Style>
            
            <Grid>
                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>

                <StackPanel x:Name="SidebarContent" Grid.Row="0" Margin="20,20,20,20">
                    <StackPanel.Style>
                        <Style TargetType="StackPanel">
                            <Setter Property="Opacity" Value="1"/>
                            <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                            <Style.Triggers>
                                <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsSidebarCollapsed}" Value="True">
                                    <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                        <BeginStoryboard>
                                            <Storyboard>
                                                <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.1"/>
                                                <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.1">
                                                    <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Collapsed}"/>
                                                </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                            </Storyboard>
                                        </BeginStoryboard>
                                    </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                    <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                        <BeginStoryboard>
                                            <Storyboard>
                                                <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.2">
                                                    <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                                </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                                <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.2" BeginTime="0:0:0.2"/>
                                            </Storyboard>
                                        </BeginStoryboard>
                                    </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                </DataTrigger>
                            </Style.Triggers>
                        </Style>
                    </StackPanel.Style>
                    <TextBlock Text="资源管理" 
                              FontSize="20" 
                              FontWeight="Bold" 
                              Foreground="White"
                              Margin="15,0,0,20"/>
                    
                    <StackPanel.Resources>
                        <!-- New Style for the long-strip toggle button -->
                        <Style x:Key="SidebarToggleStyle" TargetType="ToggleButton">
                            <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                            <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
                            <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="White"/>
                            <Setter Property="HorizontalContentAlignment" Value="Left"/>
                            <Setter Property="FontSize" Value="15"/>
                            <Setter Property="Padding" Value="20,12"/>
                            <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,0,0,20"/>
                            <Setter Property="Cursor" Value="Hand"/>
                            <Setter Property="Template">
                                <Setter.Value>
                                    <ControlTemplate TargetType="ToggleButton">
                                        <Border x:Name="border" 
                                                Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" 
                                                CornerRadius="16">
                                            <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                                                <Border Width="19"/> <!-- Indent to match RadioButtons which have indicators -->
                                                <ContentPresenter VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </Border>
                                        <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#10FFFFFF"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#25FFFFFF"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                        </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    </ControlTemplate>
                                </Setter.Value>
                            </Setter>
                        </Style>
                    </StackPanel.Resources>

                    <!-- The new "long strip" toggle button -->
                    <ToggleButton Content="⬅️  收起侧栏" 
                                Style="{StaticResource SidebarToggleStyle}"
                                IsChecked="{Binding IsSidebarCollapsed}"/>

                <StackPanel>
                    <StackPanel.Triggers>
                        <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="RadioButton.Checked">
                            <BeginStoryboard>
                                <Storyboard>
                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="RightContentArea" Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" From="0" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.4">
                                        <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                            <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseOut"/>
                                        </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                    </DoubleAnimation>
                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetName="RightContentArea" Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TranslateTransform.Y)" From="20" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.4">
                                        <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                            <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseOut"/>
                                        </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                    </DoubleAnimation>
                                </Storyboard>
                            </BeginStoryboard>
                        </EventTrigger>
                    </StackPanel.Triggers>

                    <StackPanel.Resources>
                            <!-- ToggleButton style for active state -->
                            <Style x:Key="CategoryToggle" TargetType="RadioButton">
                                <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                                <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
                                <Setter Property="Foreground" Value="White"/>
                                <Setter Property="HorizontalContentAlignment" Value="Left"/>
                                <Setter Property="FontSize" Value="16"/>
                                <Setter Property="Padding" Value="20,16"/>
                                <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,0,0,8"/>
                                <Setter Property="Cursor" Value="Hand"/>
                                <Setter Property="Template">
                                    <Setter.Value>
                                        <ControlTemplate TargetType="RadioButton">
                                            <Border x:Name="border" 
                                                    Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" 
                                                    CornerRadius="16">
                                                <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                                                    <!-- Selection Indicator -->
                                                    <Border x:Name="indicator" 
                                                            Width="4" Height="20" 
                                                            Background="#00E676" 
                                                            CornerRadius="2" 
                                                            Margin="0,0,15,0"
                                                            Visibility="Hidden"/>
                                                    <ContentPresenter Margin="0,0,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </Border>
                                            <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                                <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                                    <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#10FFFFFF"/>
                                                </Trigger>
                                                <Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="True">
                                                    <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#25FFFFFF"/>
                                                    <Setter TargetName="indicator" Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                                                    <Setter Property="FontWeight" Value="SemiBold"/>
                                                </Trigger>
                                            </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                        </ControlTemplate>
                                    </Setter.Value>
                                </Setter>
                            </Style>
                        </StackPanel.Resources>

                        <RadioButton Content="🧩  Mod " 
                                   Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                                   IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=mod}"
                                   Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                                   CommandParameter="mod"/>
                        
                        <RadioButton Content="📦  整合包" 
                                   Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                                   IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=modpack}"
                                   Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                                   CommandParameter="modpack"/>
                        
                        <RadioButton Content="🖼️  资源包" 
                                   Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                                   IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=resourcepack}"
                                   Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                                   CommandParameter="resourcepack"/>
                        
                        <RadioButton Content="☀️  光影包" 
                                   Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                                   IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=shader}"
                                   Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                                   CommandParameter="shader"/>
                        
                        <RadioButton Content="🏷️  数据包" 
                                   Style="{StaticResource CategoryToggle}"
                                   IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=datapack}"
                                   Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                                   CommandParameter="datapack"/>
                                   
                        <!-- Sidebar View More Button -->
                        <Button Command="{Binding ViewMoreCommand}" 
                                Margin="0,20,0,0"
                                Background="#15FFFFFF" 
                                Foreground="White"
                                HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                BorderThickness="0"
                                Cursor="Hand"
                                Height="45">
                            <Button.Template>
                                <ControlTemplate TargetType="Button">
                                    <Border x:Name="border" Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" CornerRadius="12">
                                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center">
                                            <TextBlock Text="查看全部" FontWeight="SemiBold" Margin="0,0,8,0"/>
                                            <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowRight24" FontSize="14"/>
                                        </StackPanel>
                                    </Border>
                                    <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                        <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                            <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#25FFFFFF"/>
                                        </Trigger>
                                    </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                </ControlTemplate>
                            </Button.Template>
                        </Button>
                    </StackPanel>
                </StackPanel>

                <!-- COLLAPSED SIDEBAR CONTENT (Circular Icons) -->
                <StackPanel x:Name="CollapsedSidebarContent" 
                            Grid.Row="0" 
                            Margin="0,20,0,20" 
                            HorizontalAlignment="Center">
                    <StackPanel.Style>
                        <Style TargetType="StackPanel">
                            <Setter Property="Opacity" Value="0"/>
                            <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                            <Style.Triggers>
                                <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsSidebarCollapsed}" Value="True">
                                    <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                        <BeginStoryboard>
                                            <Storyboard>
                                                <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.2">
                                                    <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                                </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                                <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.2" BeginTime="0:0:0.2"/>
                                            </Storyboard>
                                        </BeginStoryboard>
                                    </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                    <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                        <BeginStoryboard>
                                            <Storyboard>
                                                <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.1"/>
                                                <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.1">
                                                    <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Collapsed}"/>
                                                </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                            </Storyboard>
                                        </BeginStoryboard>
                                    </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                </DataTrigger>
                            </Style.Triggers>
                        </Style>
                    </StackPanel.Style>
                    
                    <!-- Circular Icon Toggle for Collapsed State -->
                    <ToggleButton IsChecked="{Binding IsSidebarCollapsed}"
                                  Width="42" Height="42"
                                  Margin="0,0,0,25"
                                  Background="#20FFFFFF"
                                  Cursor="Hand"
                                  ToolTip="展开侧栏">
                        <ToggleButton.Template>
                            <ControlTemplate TargetType="ToggleButton">
                                <Border Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" CornerRadius="21">
                                    <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="PanelLeftExpand20" FontSize="18"/>
                                </Border>
                            </ControlTemplate>
                        </ToggleButton.Template>
                    </ToggleButton>
                    <StackPanel.Resources>
                        <Style x:Key="CollapsedCategoryToggle" TargetType="RadioButton">
                            <Setter Property="Background" Value="Transparent"/>
                            <Setter Property="BorderThickness" Value="0"/>
                            <Setter Property="Width" Value="42"/>
                            <Setter Property="Height" Value="42"/>
                            <Setter Property="Margin" Value="0,0,0,12"/>
                            <Setter Property="Cursor" Value="Hand"/>
                            <Setter Property="Template">
                                <Setter.Value>
                                    <ControlTemplate TargetType="RadioButton">
                                        <Border x:Name="border" 
                                                Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" 
                                                CornerRadius="21">
                                            <ContentPresenter HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                                        </Border>
                                        <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#15FFFFFF"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                            <Trigger Property="IsChecked" Value="True">
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#30FFFFFF"/>
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="BorderBrush" Value="#00E676"/>
                                                <Setter TargetName="border" Property="BorderThickness" Value="1"/>
                                            </Trigger>
                                        </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    </ControlTemplate>
                                </Setter.Value>
                            </Setter>
                        </Style>
                    </StackPanel.Resources>

                    <!-- Circular Icon Buttons -->
                    <RadioButton Content="🧩" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CollapsedCategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=mod}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="mod"
                               ToolTip="Mod"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="📦" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CollapsedCategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=modpack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="modpack"
                               ToolTip="整合包"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="🖼️" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CollapsedCategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=resourcepack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="resourcepack"
                               ToolTip="资源包"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="☀️" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CollapsedCategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=shader}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="shader"
                               ToolTip="光影包"/>
                    
                    <RadioButton Content="🏷️" 
                               Style="{StaticResource CollapsedCategoryToggle}"
                               IsChecked="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource StringMatchToBoolConverter}, ConverterParameter=datapack}"
                               Command="{Binding SwitchCategoryCommand}"
                               CommandParameter="datapack"
                               ToolTip="数据包"/>
                               
                    <Button Command="{Binding ViewMoreCommand}" 
                            Margin="0,15,0,0"
                            Background="#15FFFFFF" 
                            Width="42" Height="42"
                            Cursor="Hand"
                            ToolTip="查看全部">
                        <Button.Template>
                            <ControlTemplate TargetType="Button">
                                <Border x:Name="border" Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" CornerRadius="21">
                                    <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowRight24" FontSize="16" Foreground="White"/>
                                </Border>
                                <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                        <Setter TargetName="border" Property="Background" Value="#25FFFFFF"/>
                                    </Trigger>
                                </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                            </ControlTemplate>
                        </Button.Template>
                    </Button>
                </StackPanel>
            </Grid>
        </Border>

        <!-- RIGHT CONTENT AREA -->
        <Grid x:Name="RightContentArea" Grid.Column="1" Margin="40,30,40,30" RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5">
            <Grid.RenderTransform>
                <TransformGroup>
                    <ScaleTransform/>
                    <TranslateTransform/>
                </TransformGroup>
            </Grid.RenderTransform>
            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
            </Grid.RowDefinitions>

            <!-- Header Section -->
            <StackPanel Grid.Row="0" Margin="0,0,0,30">
                <!-- Title Row -->
                <Grid Margin="0,0,0,20">
                    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

                    <StackPanel Grid.Column="0">
                        <TextBlock Text="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource CategoryNameConverter}}" 
                                 FontSize="36" 
                                 FontWeight="Bold" 
                                 Foreground="White"
                                 Margin="0,0,0,8"/>
                        <TextBlock Text="从 Modrinth 仓库搜索和下载资源。" 
                                 FontSize="16" 
                                 Foreground="#CCFFFFFF"/>
                    </StackPanel>

                    <!-- Import Button -->
                    <ui:Button Grid.Column="1"
                               VerticalAlignment="Top"
                               Content="导入 .mrpack"
                               Appearance="Primary"
                               Command="{Binding ImportModpackCommand}"
                               Padding="15,8"
                               FontSize="14">
                        <ui:Button.Icon>
                            <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowImport24"/>
                        </ui:Button.Icon>
                    </ui:Button>
                </Grid>
                    
                <!-- Search Bar Card -->
                <Border Background="#30252525" 
                        BorderBrush="#50FFFFFF"
                        BorderThickness="1"
                        CornerRadius="24"
                        Padding="20,12">
                    <Border.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="20" ShadowDepth="0" Opacity="0.15" Color="Black"/>
                    </Border.Effect>
                    
                    <Grid>
                        <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                            <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                            <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                        </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                        
                        <!-- Search TextBox -->
                        <TextBox Grid.Column="0"
                                 Text="{Binding SearchQuery, UpdateSourceTrigger=PropertyChanged}"
                                 FontSize="18"
                                 VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                 Background="Transparent"
                                 BorderThickness="0"
                                 Foreground="#EEEEEE"
                                 CaretBrush="#00E676"
                                 Padding="5,8">
                            <TextBox.InputBindings>
                                <KeyBinding Key="Return" Command="{Binding SearchCommand}"/>
                            </TextBox.InputBindings>
                        </TextBox>
                        
                        <!-- Search Button -->
                        <ui:Button Grid.Column="1"
                                  Command="{Binding SearchCommand}"
                                  Content="🔍 搜索"
                                  Appearance="Secondary"
                                  Margin="10,0,0,0"
                                  Padding="25,10"
                                  FontSize="14"
                                  Foreground="#EEEEEE"/>
                    </Grid>
                </Border>
                
                <!-- Progress Bar -->
                <ProgressBar IsIndeterminate="{Binding IsBusy}" 
                            Height="2" 
                            Margin="0,10,0,0"
                            Visibility="{Binding IsBusy, Converter={StaticResource BooleanToVisibilityConverter}}"
                            Background="Transparent" 
                            BorderThickness="0" 
                            Foreground="#00E676"/>
            </StackPanel>

            <!-- Main Content Area -->
            <ScrollViewer Grid.Row="1" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled">
                <Grid>
                    <!-- ========== FEATURED SECTIONS (when no search) ========== -->
                    <StackPanel>
                        <StackPanel.Style>
                            <Style TargetType="StackPanel">
                                <Setter Property="Opacity" Value="1"/>
                                <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Visible"/>
                                <Style.Triggers>
                                    <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding HasSearchResults}" Value="True">
                                        <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                            <BeginStoryboard>
                                                <Storyboard>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                                    <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.3">
                                                        <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Collapsed}"/>
                                                    </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                                </Storyboard>
                                            </BeginStoryboard>
                                        </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                        <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                            <BeginStoryboard>
                                                <Storyboard>
                                                    <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility">
                                                        <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                                    </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                                    <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                                </Storyboard>
                                            </BeginStoryboard>
                                        </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                    </DataTrigger>
                                </Style.Triggers>
                            </Style>
                        </StackPanel.Style>
                        
                        <!-- 🔥 Trending Section -->
                        <Grid Margin="0,10,0,15">
                             <TextBlock Text="🔥 热门推荐" 
                                     FontSize="20" 
                                     FontWeight="Bold" 
                                     Foreground="White"
                                     VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                     HorizontalAlignment="Left"/>
                        </Grid>
                        <ScrollViewer HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Margin="0,0,0,30"
                                      PreviewMouseWheel="ScrollViewer_PreviewMouseWheel">
                            <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding TrendingMods}">
                                <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal"/>
                                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                    <DataTemplate>
                                        <Border Width="180" Height="260" Margin="0,0,15,0" 
                                                CornerRadius="16" 
                                                Background="#40252525" 
                                                BorderBrush="#50FFFFFF" 
                                                BorderThickness="1"
                                                RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5"
                                                Cursor="Hand">
                                            <Border.RenderTransform>
                                                <TransformGroup>
                                                    <ScaleTransform/>
                                                    <TranslateTransform/>
                                                </TransformGroup>
                                            </Border.RenderTransform>
                                            <Border.Effect>
                                                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="15" ShadowDepth="3" Opacity="0.3" Color="Black"/>
                                            </Border.Effect>
                                            <Border.Triggers>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseEnter">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="-3" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseLeave">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                            </Border.Triggers>
                                            <Grid>
                                                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="110"/>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                                    <Border.Background>
                                                        <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                                    </Border.Background>
                                                </Border>
                                                <StackPanel Grid.Row="1" Margin="12,10,12,12">
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14" Foreground="White" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis" Margin="0,0,0,4"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" Margin="0,0,0,6"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Summary}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#80FFFFFF" TextWrapping="Wrap" MaxHeight="40" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                    <ui:Button Content="⬇️ 下载"
                                                               Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                               CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                               Appearance="Primary"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                               Margin="0,8,0,0"
                                                               Padding="0,6"
                                                               FontSize="12"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </Border>
                                    </DataTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl>
                        </ScrollViewer>

                        <!-- ✨ Newest Section -->
                        <Grid Margin="0,0,0,15">
                             <TextBlock Text="✨ 最新发布" 
                                     FontSize="20" 
                                     FontWeight="Bold" 
                                     Foreground="White"
                                     VerticalAlignment="Center"
                                     HorizontalAlignment="Left"/>
                        </Grid>
                        <ScrollViewer HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled" Margin="0,0,0,30"
                                      PreviewMouseWheel="ScrollViewer_PreviewMouseWheel">
                            <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding NewestMods}">
                                <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                    <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal"/>
                                    </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                    <DataTemplate>
                                        <Border Width="180" Height="260" Margin="0,0,15,0" 
                                                CornerRadius="16" 
                                                Background="#40252525" 
                                                BorderBrush="#50FFFFFF" 
                                                BorderThickness="1"
                                                RenderTransformOrigin="0.5,0.5"
                                                Cursor="Hand">
                                            <Border.RenderTransform>
                                                <TransformGroup>
                                                    <ScaleTransform/>
                                                    <TranslateTransform/>
                                                </TransformGroup>
                                            </Border.RenderTransform>
                                            <Border.Effect>
                                                <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="15" ShadowDepth="3" Opacity="0.3" Color="Black"/>
                                            </Border.Effect>
                                            <Border.Triggers>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseEnter">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.04" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="-3" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                                <EventTrigger RoutedEvent="MouseLeave">
                                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                                        <Storyboard>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleX)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[0].(ScaleTransform.ScaleY)" To="1.0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TransformGroup.Children)[1].(TranslateTransform.Y)" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.2"/>
                                                        </Storyboard>
                                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                                </EventTrigger>
                                            </Border.Triggers>
                                            <Grid>
                                                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="110"/>
                                                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                                </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                                    <Border.Background>
                                                        <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                                    </Border.Background>
                                                </Border>
                                                <StackPanel Grid.Row="1" Margin="12,10,12,12">
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14" Foreground="White" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis" Margin="0,0,0,4"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" Margin="0,0,0,6"/>
                                                    <TextBlock Text="{Binding Summary}" FontSize="12" Foreground="#80FFFFFF" TextWrapping="Wrap" MaxHeight="40" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                    <ui:Button Content="⬇️ 下载"
                                                               Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                               CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                               Appearance="Primary"
                                                               HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                               Margin="0,8,0,0"
                                                               Padding="0,6"
                                                               FontSize="12"/>
                                                </StackPanel>
                                            </Grid>
                                        </Border>
                                    </DataTemplate>
                                </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl>
                        </ScrollViewer>
                    </StackPanel>

                    <!-- ========== SEARCH RESULTS (Replaced by Full Page View) ========== -->
                    <!-- Keeping this empty/hidden as search results now go to full page view or we can keep a mini version? 
                         User asked for "View More" to jump to a full page.
                         If user searches via Search Bar, where should results go?
                         Ideally, search also triggers Full Page View. -->
                    
                    
                </Grid> <!-- End internal Grid -->
            </ScrollViewer> <!-- End internal ScrollViewer -->
        </Grid> <!-- End RightContentArea -->
    </Grid> <!-- End DashboardLayer -->

    <!-- FULL PAGE VIEW (Overlay) -->
    <Grid x:Name="FullPageViewOverlay"
          Grid.Row="0" Grid.RowSpan="2" Grid.Column="0" Grid.ColumnSpan="2"
          Background="#40000000"> <!-- iOS Casting Style: Darker translucency for full window coverage -->
                <Grid.Style>
                    <Style TargetType="Grid">
                        <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                        <Setter Property="Opacity" Value="0"/>
                        <Style.Triggers>
                            <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsFullPageView}" Value="True">
                                <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                        <Storyboard>
                                            <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility">
                                                <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                            </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TranslateTransform.Y)" From="50" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.4">
                                                <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                                    <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseOut"/>
                                                </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                            </DoubleAnimation>
                                        </Storyboard>
                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                        <Storyboard>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                            <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.3">
                                                <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Collapsed}"/>
                                            </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                        </Storyboard>
                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                            </DataTrigger>
                        </Style.Triggers>
                    </Style>
                </Grid.Style>
                <Grid.RenderTransform>
                    <TranslateTransform/>
                </Grid.RenderTransform>

                <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                    <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
                    <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                </Grid.RowDefinitions>

                <!-- Header -->
                <Grid Grid.Row="0" Margin="25,30,25,20">
                    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
                        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
                    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>

                    <!-- Back Button -->
                    <Button Command="{Binding GoBackCommand}"
                            Background="Transparent"
                            BorderThickness="0"
                            HorizontalAlignment="Left"
                            VerticalAlignment="Center"
                            Cursor="Hand"
                            Padding="8">
                        <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">
                            <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowLeft24" FontSize="24" Foreground="White"/>
                            <TextBlock Text="返回" FontSize="18" FontWeight="SemiBold" Foreground="White" Margin="10,0,0,0" VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                        </StackPanel>
                        <Button.Template>
                            <ControlTemplate TargetType="Button">
                                <Border Background="{TemplateBinding Background}" CornerRadius="8" Padding="{TemplateBinding Padding}">
                                    <ContentPresenter/>
                                </Border>
                                <ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                                    <Trigger Property="IsMouseOver" Value="True">
                                        <Setter Property="Background" Value="#15FFFFFF"/>
                                    </Trigger>
                                </ControlTemplate.Triggers>
                            </ControlTemplate>
                        </Button.Template>
                    </Button>

                    <!-- Title -->
                    <TextBlock Grid.Column="1" 
                               Style="{StaticResource iOS26.Text.Title}"
                               Text="{Binding SelectedCategory, Converter={StaticResource CategoryNameConverter}, StringFormat='所有 {0}'}" 
                               HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                               VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                </Grid>

                <!-- Content -->
                <ScrollViewer Grid.Row="1" Margin="20,0,20,30">
                    <StackPanel>
                        <ItemsControl ItemsSource="{Binding SearchResults}">
                            <ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                                <ItemsPanelTemplate>
                                    <WrapPanel Orientation="Horizontal" HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
                                </ItemsPanelTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl.ItemsPanel>
                            <ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                                <DataTemplate>
                                    <!-- Simplified Card for Grid View (Optimized for 5 Columns: 146x210) -->
                                     <Border Width="146" Height="210" Margin="5" 
                                            CornerRadius="16" 
                                            Background="{StaticResource iOS26.CardLayer}" 
                                            BorderBrush="#40FFFFFF" 
                                            BorderThickness="1"
                                            Cursor="Hand">
                                        <Border.Effect>
                                            <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="10" ShadowDepth="2" Opacity="0.2" Color="Black"/>
                                        </Border.Effect>
                                        <Grid>
                                            <Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="85"/>
                                                <RowDefinition Height="*"/>
                                            </Grid.RowDefinitions>
                                            <Border Grid.Row="0" CornerRadius="16,16,0,0" ClipToBounds="True">
                                                <Border.Background>
                                                    <ImageBrush ImageSource="{Binding IconUrl}" Stretch="UniformToFill"/>
                                                </Border.Background>
                                            </Border>
                                            <StackPanel Grid.Row="1" Margin="8,6">
                                                <TextBlock Text="{Binding Name}" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="12" Foreground="White" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                <TextBlock Text="{Binding Author}" FontSize="10" Foreground="#A0FFFFFF" Margin="0,1,0,3" TextTrimming="CharacterEllipsis"/>
                                                <ui:Button Content="下载"
                                                           Command="{Binding DataContext.DownloadModCommand, RelativeSource={RelativeSource AncestorType=Page}}"
                                                           CommandParameter="{Binding}"
                                                           Appearance="Primary"
                                                           HorizontalAlignment="Stretch"
                                                           Margin="0,2,0,0"
                                                           Padding="0,4"
                                                           FontSize="11"/>
                                            </StackPanel>
                                        </Grid>
                                    </Border>
                                </DataTemplate>
                            </ItemsControl.ItemTemplate>
                        </ItemsControl>

                        <!-- Load More Button -->
                        <Button Content="加载更多" 
                                Command="{Binding LoadMoreCommand}" 
                                Style="{StaticResource iOS26.SecondaryButton}"
                                HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                                Margin="0,20,0,20"
                                Padding="40,12"
                                FontSize="16"/>
                    </StackPanel>
                </ScrollViewer>
            </Grid>

            <!-- Import Progress Overlay -->
            <Grid Grid.Row="0" Grid.RowSpan="2" 
                  Background="#30000000"
                  Grid.ColumnSpan="2">
                <Grid.Style>
                    <Style TargetType="Grid">
                        <Setter Property="Visibility" Value="Collapsed"/>
                        <Setter Property="Opacity" Value="0"/>
                        <Style.Triggers>
                            <DataTrigger Binding="{Binding IsImporting}" Value="True">
                                <DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                        <Storyboard>
                                            <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility">
                                                <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Visible}"/>
                                            </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="1" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="(UIElement.RenderTransform).(TranslateTransform.Y)" From="30" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.4">
                                                <DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                                    <CubicEase EasingMode="EaseOut"/>
                                                </DoubleAnimation.EasingFunction>
                                            </DoubleAnimation>
                                        </Storyboard>
                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                </DataTrigger.EnterActions>
                                <DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                                    <BeginStoryboard>
                                        <Storyboard>
                                            <DoubleAnimation Storyboard.TargetProperty="Opacity" To="0" Duration="0:0:0.3"/>
                                            <ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames Storyboard.TargetProperty="Visibility" BeginTime="0:0:0.3">
                                                <DiscreteObjectKeyFrame KeyTime="0" Value="{x:Static Visibility.Collapsed}"/>
                                            </ObjectAnimationUsingKeyFrames>
                                        </Storyboard>
                                    </BeginStoryboard>
                                </DataTrigger.ExitActions>
                            </DataTrigger>
                        </Style.Triggers>
                    </Style>
                </Grid.Style>
                <Grid.RenderTransform>
                    <TranslateTransform/>
                </Grid.RenderTransform>

                <Border Background="#252525" 
                        BorderBrush="#40FFFFFF" 
                        BorderThickness="1" 
                        CornerRadius="16"
                        HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                        VerticalAlignment="Center"
                        Padding="30"
                        MinWidth="320">
                    <Border.Effect>
                        <DropShadowEffect BlurRadius="20" ShadowDepth="0" Opacity="0.5" Color="Black"/>
                    </Border.Effect>
                    <StackPanel>
                        <ui:SymbolIcon Symbol="ArrowImport24" FontSize="48" Foreground="White" Margin="0,0,0,15"/>
                        <TextBlock Text="正在导入整合包" 
                                   FontSize="20" 
                                   FontWeight="SemiBold" 
                                   Foreground="White" 
                                   HorizontalAlignment="Center" 
                                   Margin="0,0,0,20"/>
                        
                        <ProgressBar Value="{Binding ImportProgress}" 
                                     Maximum="100" 
                                     Height="4" 
                                     Foreground="#00E676"
                                     Background="#33FFFFFF"
                                     BorderThickness="0"
                                     Margin="0,0,0,10"/>
                        
                        <TextBlock Text="{Binding ImportStatus}" 
                                   FontSize="13" 
                                   Foreground="#B0FFFFFF" 
                                   HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
                    </StackPanel>
                </Border>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
</Page>
